Writer:  Paul Levitz
Artists:  Keith Giffen and Larry Mahlstedt
Letterer:  Annette Kawecki; John Costanza
Colorist:  Carl Gafford

The Great Darkness Sage - Part 2

Upon capturing on of the thieves, the legion run tests to discover what kind of creature it is. The DNA reveals it is a native of Talok VII and not only that, its Shadow Lass' dead ancestor Lydea Mallor. Mordru becomes the latest victim in the hunt for magic. Dream Girl takes the team to meet her sister, Mysa, The White Witch when a servant of the darkness attempts to abduct her. It fails and Dream Girl gets a vision of the Legion's final battle.

In the second story Saturn Girl tends to Lightning Lad and Dream Girl is announced as leader. Lydea awakes.

